metadata.name: Turtle Town #1
metadata.description: Turtle Town is a collection of 10,000 cute and cool turtles on the Ethereum Blockchain who like to hang out at the beach, fish, cause mischief, and play games! Holders can help protect Turtle Town from a group of grumpy and mean crocodiles called the Crooked Crocs to earn rewards! You won't want to miss out on this awesome adventure!
